Package: septa.org
Title: SEPTA Transit Real-Time Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for SEPTA (Southeastern Pennsylvania Transportation Authority)
    real-time APIs. Get train positions, bus locations, alerts, elevator outages, and detours.
    Includes LLM context injection via septa_context().
